<p>Peeks the specified address in parameter 1 + parameter 2 and returns the value.</p>
<p><strong>Examples:</strong></p>
<p><code>border := peek(^$D020, 0); // Red border color</code></p>
<p><code>
some_val = peek(my_array, 3); // Set 3rd element of array to 10.
// Same as:
some_val := my_array[3];
</code><</p>
